{"tid":1714042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你返工","createTime":"2019-11-12T23:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:21:14.000Z","uid":223609,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59b802b14c43c256ff39cfb001ab7a594df1350a","tid":1714042,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"我同太太最愛返工，今日會渣一人一部車返工，<br />\n<br />\n由九龍西渣到香港東，再返香港西，入東涌，再去元朗，先出返中環。<br />\n <br />\n預計下午6點會返到公司先收工。<br />\n<br />\n希望所有有車既香港人同我地一樣熱愛返工。<br />\n<br />\n渣車係馬路又安全又合法，記得唔好超速（40max)，車距要保持5米呀。"},{"pid":"5754e9c9f4a12e8cf94bb05db8e188bec2581990","tid":1714042,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:31:32.000Z","msg":"啲交通燈壞晒 個個司機轉彎都唔讓車 咁會塞死晒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有車嘅手足請入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1709403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1709403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b36a0c070e64054a11e02dd330c86d32c547caf","tid":1714042,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:35:34.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"7987b2ffd79fe27b4e9c22d8b4ce50ce216b8783","tid":1714042,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5754e9c9f4a12e8cf94bb05db8e188bec2581990","tid":1714042,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:31:32.000Z","msg":"啲交通燈壞晒 個個司機轉彎都唔讓車 咁會塞死晒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有車嘅手足請入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1709403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1709403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b543ec2ce3b99d16a29cca58f6ed5f72f54240","tid":1714042,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7987b2ffd79fe27b4e9c22d8b4ce50ce216b8783","tid":1714042,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q